title: Bani J’s Cute Selfie With Beau Yuvraj Thakur Shuts All Break-Up Rumours
text:
facebook 
After this season of Bigg Boss ended, a lot of speculation was rife about the lives and relationships of the contestants. The most talked about has to be that of Bani J and whether she was still dating long time beau Yuvraj Thakur, or not! Sometime ago we did inform you that that Bani put up a picture of Yuvraj , putting all the rumours to an end. But, as the celeb life goes, the rumours erupted again and but we stumbled upon another selfies of the two lovebirds on Instagram, making everything crystal clear once again. 
The two are in the gym doing what they love the most. We are glad to see that there is no trouble in paradise!
